title.rendered: Yea Toh Two Much Ho Gayaa

content.rendered:
Directed by Anwer Khan.

Written by Anwer Khan. Anwer Khan. Bolu Khan.

Cast Jimmy Shergill(Mann / Mohan). Pooja Chopra(Meena). Arbaaz Khan(Mak). Bruna Abdullah(Tina). Murli Sharma(Choudhary). Zarina Wahab(Amma). Srikant Maski(Bheema). Vijay Patkar(Tun / Pintu) . Sanndeep Basu(Sarpanch).Sandeep Bose. Mahsa Kooshesh(Item Girl). Nancy Marwah(Radha (as Nancy)). Ohyeakash(Goon). Dev Sharma(Dev). Devanshu Sharma(Dev). Maushmi Udeshi(Sapna). Di Viola(Sayna)

Language Hindi.

Producers Sahni Bob. Badshah Khan. Nillay Pande. Rushita Singh. Ali Unwala.

Production Trinity Films.
